âž¡ A place where Git stores project history.

ðŸ”¹ Intermediate

Q4. Difference between git fetch and git pull?
    fetch â†’ downloads only
    pull â†’ fetch + merge

Q5. What is HEAD?
âž¡ Pointer to the current commit.

Q6. What is staging area?
âž¡ Intermediate area before commit.

ðŸ”¹ Advanced

Q7. What is rebase?
âž¡ Rewrites commit history to keep it linear.

Q8. What is cherry-pick?
âž¡ Apply a specific commit from another branch.

Q9. How to undo a commit?
git reset --soft HEAD~1
git reset --hard HEAD~1
git revert <commit-id>

âœ… 2ï¸âƒ£ Git Rebase vs Merge (VERY IMPORTANT)
ðŸ”¹ Conceptual Difference
| Feature               | Rebase        | Merge       |
| --------------------- | ------------- | ----------- |
| History               | Linear        | Branching   |
| Commits               | Rewritten     | Preserved   |
| Safe on shared branch | âŒ             | âœ…           |
| Used for              | Clean history | Team safety |

ðŸ”¹ Merge Example
