GitHub repository already has commits : 
----------------------------------------

Step 1: Pull remote changes first
git pull origin main --allow-unrelated-histories

--> ðŸ“Œ --allow-unrelated-histories is needed because:
--> Local repo and remote repo were created separately

Step 2: Resolve merge (if asked)
git add .
git commit -m "Merge remote and local changes"

Step 3: Push again
git push -u origin main
